qualifications to lead the $850 billion Department of Defense and its 2.7 m=
illion service members and civilians. In short, Rieckhoff told me, Hegseth=
=E2=80=99s appeal for Republicans isn=E2=80=99t his
management experience=E2=80=94which is minimal=E2=80=94but rather his right=
-wing ideology, formidable communication skills, and talent for generating =
media soundbites. Alas, Rieckhoff argued, the Pentagon should be the least =
