s host whom <b>Donald Trump </b>has nominated for secretary of defense, ran=
 two veterans groups that were overtly conservative. <br/><br/>Not surprisi=
ngly, when I invited Rieckhoff on my podcast, <i>Somebody=E2=80=99s Gotta W=
