             <td style=3D"padding-bottom: 36px; color: #000000; font-size: =
16px; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;"><b>How do you th=
ink this will impact the morale within the Department of Defense?</b><br/><=
br/>It basically calcifies a certain ideology. For instance, if you=E2=80=
=99re a right-wing MAGA guy and you like Christian nationalism and don=E2=
