aging, especially to the professional corps of officers who are
supposed to be beyond politics.<br/><br/><b>There=E2=80=99s a lot of genera=
l distrust regarding the military industrial complex. Do you think that any=
 of Pete Hegseth=E2=80=99s disruption will do any good for the institution?=
</b><br/><br/>Maybe, but at what expense? Removing corruption and tackling =
